OL,6,GThe axing of Hardtalk in the latest
OL,7,Ground of BBC cuts has caused
OL,8,Gcontroversy.
OL,10,FIt is hard to pretend that the loss of
OL,11,Fthis in-depth interview programme is
OL,12,Fanything but a disappointing response
OL,13,Fto financial necessity.
OL,15,FIt often features people of
OL,16,Finternational note and interviews
OL,17,Fwhich probe their subjects properly.
OL,19,FBut is it really such a blow to UK
OL,20,Fviewers?
