OL,6,FThe risk of domestic BBC News and
OL,7,FCurrent Affairs simply suffering a
OL,8,Fdeath by a thousand cuts is much more
OL,9,Fserious than the axing of a programme
OL,10,Fwith a low UK audience.
OL,12,FNewsnight in its traditional form,
OL,13,Flocal radio, a dedicated domestic news
OL,14,Fchannel ` what next?
