OL,13,Fit really so bad for national radio
OL,14,Fstations to share news summaries.
OL,16,FBut maybe there needs to be a renewed
OL,17,Ffocus on maintaining the quality of
OL,18,Fthe core TV output? Especially when it
OL,19,Fcomes to deeper content rather than
OL,20,Fstraight news.
